FiddleSticks.name: Fiddlesticks
FiddleSticks.title: the Ancient Fear
FiddleSticks.lore: Something has awoken in Runeterra. Something ancient. Something terrible. The ageless horror known as Fiddlesticks stalks the edges of mortal society, drawn to areas thick with paranoia where it feeds upon terrorized victims. Wielding a jagged scythe, the haggard, makeshift creature reaps fear itself, shattering the minds of those unlucky enough to survive in its wake. Beware the sounding of the crow, or the whispering of the shape that appears almost human… Fiddlesticks has returned.
FiddleSticks.blurb: Something has awoken in Runeterra. Something ancient. Something terrible. The ageless horror known as Fiddlesticks stalks the edges of mortal society, drawn to areas thick with paranoia where it feeds upon terrorized victims. Wielding a jagged scythe...

spells.name: Terrify
spells.description: Fiddlesticks damaging enemies with spells while unseen or targeting an enemy with Terrify's activation strikes a target unit with fear, causing it to flee in terror for a duration.
spells.tooltip:
Passive: While unseen and out of combat or posing as an Effigy, damaging an enemy with a spell terrifies them for {{ fearduration }} seconds.

Active: Terrifies a target for {{ fearduration }} seconds and deals {{ maxhealthdamage*100 }}% (+1% per 50AP) of the target's current health (minimum {{ minimumdamage }}) as magic damage.

If the target has recently been terrified, instead deal {{ maxhealthdamage*200 }}% (+2% per 50AP) of the target's current health (minimum {{ minimumdamage*2 }}) as magic damage.

Max 400 damage vs monsters.

spells.name: Bountiful Harvest
spells.description: Fiddlesticks drains health from nearby enemies, dealing bonus execute damage at the end of the duration.
spells.tooltip:
Drains the souls of nearby enemies, dealing {{ draindamagecalc }} magic damage per second over 2 seconds plus {{ percentfortooltip }}% of their missing health on the final instance of damage.

Fiddlesticks heals for {{ vamppercentage }}% of the damage dealt before mitigation, reduced to {{ minionhealingmod }}% vs minions.

On a completed channel or if nothing remains to be harvested, refund 60% of the remaining cooldown.

Damage dealt to minions is reduced to {{ miniondamagemod*100 }}%

spells.name: Reap
spells.description: Fiddlesticks slashes an area with its scythe, slowing all enemies hit and silencing enemies hit in the center of the slash.
spells.tooltip:
Unleash dark magic at a target position, dealing {{ damage }} magic damage to and slowing enemies hit by {{ slowamount*-100 }}% for {{ silenceduration }} seconds in a crescent shaped area.

Enemies in the center of the crescent are silenced for the duration as well as slowed.

spells.name: Crowstorm
spells.description: A murder of crows flock wildly around Fiddlesticks, dealing damage per second to all enemy units in the area.
spells.tooltip:
Channel for {{ channeltime }} seconds, then blink to the target point unleashing a murder of crows, dealing {{ damagepersecond }} (+{{ apratiotick }}) magic damage per second to all enemy units in the area.

The effect lasts for {{ duration }} seconds, dealing up to {{ totaldamage }} (+{{ apratiofullduration }}) total magic damage.

passive.name: A Harmless Scarecrow
passive.description: Fiddlesticks' trinket is replaced by scarecrow effigies.
passive.tooltip:
Fiddlesticks' trinket is replaced by Scarecrow Effigies.

Effigies gain power as Fiddlesticks levels, reducing their cooldown and increasing their duration.

Level 6: Effigies will reveal any nearby wards for 6 seconds on placement.
